Class Project

java.lang.Object
Project
public class Project extends Object
Entity.

This Project class represents a housing project with details such as name, neighbourhood,visibility, unit availability, pricing, application period, managing officer, and applicants.

  • Constructor Details

    • Project

      Project(String name, String neighbourhood, boolean visibility, int num2Rooms, int num3Rooms, String openingDate, String closingDate, int availOfficerSlots, Manager manager, int price2room, int price3room)
      Constructs a Project object with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      name - the project name
      neighbourhood - the neighbourhood of the project
      visibility - visibility status (true if visible)
      num2Rooms - number of 2-room units
      num3Rooms - number of 3-room units
      openingDate - application start date
      closingDate - application end date
      availOfficerSlots - number of available officer slots
      manager - the manager of the project
      price2room - price for 2-room units
      price3room - price for 3-room units
